name: Corneo's PoV (Bound?) Anal Missionary TI Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for a point-of-view anal sex (missionary-like) position. It was intended to also feature arms_up, bound_wrists but I struggled to find enough good training images, so instead it's only partly trained on them and you can add those tags to your prompt to produce a bound anal scene.

It's also trained with a little male-on-male and futa, so you can hopefully induce that if you want it, or add those to the negative prompt if you do not.

Example images produced with my 7th Heaven mix available here https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
